Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:11.75,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翻譯：最愛炮姐 小約 飯糰粽子   後期：sslish
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.56,0:00:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.62,0:00:12.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫現實啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:33.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 都那麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.33,0:02:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難相處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.64,0:02:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.61,0:02:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點事還不能讓我洩氣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.12,0:02:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天為了振作精神 一定要好好瘋一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露西 去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:04.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}ABC席從南門入\NDES席從北門入
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.43,0:03:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傻妞 為什麼不用羽衣隱身…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.00,0:03:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A8區52號…52…52…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.67,0:03:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 這個座位是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是這個位置
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.10,0:03:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂 桂木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老天保佑不要暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.04,0:04:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 票是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧 那麼好的座位居然重複預訂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.60,0:04:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的 別傻站著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.81,0:04:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快坐下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木同學 這個座位讓給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.68,0:04:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去找找有沒有空著的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有空位的 一人坐一半吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不行啦 老師怎麼可以和學生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.93,0:04:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被別人看見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.72,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快 職業摔角NOAH
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:05:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘉年華淘汰賽 最終決賽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說這個席位是很棒啦…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選手入場
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.44,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍方 秋川純 三和光張
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.32,0:05:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅方 石井角 傑布基·賈尼傑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.63,0:05:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋川是這團隊的年輕王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看你看 快看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.14,0:06:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的三和 那個人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.21,0:06:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會使出和巨漢鶴馬一樣的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用完之後也會大叫「喔~」的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好看喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.23,0:06:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.10,0:06:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就是這樣 上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:28.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的是那杯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 就差一點點了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那裡 上呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.72,0:07:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然有個好位置感受到的氣魄都不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.46,0:07:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後排的位置可感受不到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.74,0:07:50.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠的這麼近還是不好的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.94,0:07:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師和學生這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,職業摔角這麼有激情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔角手之間用盡渾身解數碰撞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.00,0:08:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而他們的一舉手一投足觀眾則會用掌聲回應
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.19,0:08:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後為之顫抖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔角能夠這麼有激情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.38,0:08:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為大家的步調都一致
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.48,0:08:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔角不僅僅是局限在擂臺上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽的裁判
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輔助著選手們的工作人員們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.21,0:09:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後和觀眾們一起創造出了這場比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家合而為一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 你為什麼就是不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明為了你考慮了這麼多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.79,0:09:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你就是不回應我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了你我連遊戲機都買了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.99,0:09:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很貴的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.29,0:09:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我一個人的話是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是大家一起努力的話是辦不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.03,0:09:46.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這個 籃球部毀了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經休部的籃球部 隊長還是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.98,0:09:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是妳那一代被毀了的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.88,0:10:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妳毀了籃球部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.94,0:10:08.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你聽說了什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:13.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我現在覺得相同的事情會再度發生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能還會有人被妳的理想所擊潰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.67,0:10:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,純 妳做的太過火了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再陪妳瘋下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明大家都說了想要變得更強的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.17,0:10:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都要離去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.68,0:10:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了籃球部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.92,0:10:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了大家 拼命的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳 真的是為了大家著想嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這話是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.66,0:11:17.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這種人又懂些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.77,0:11:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不理解我的感受
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.43,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能…看到結局了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「長瀨 大家的煩惱諮詢」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.33,0:12:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉他的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳看 如果是這個檔次的話挺便宜的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:14.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 一點都不便宜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.40,0:12:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 艾莉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.06,0:12:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說昨天  長瀨老師打電話給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.52,0:12:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 你也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.24,0:12:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 這不正是你的目的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.11,0:12:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.97,0:12:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過有點纏人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.72,0:12:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近有些微妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長瀨老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前還發生過那樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.83,0:12:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 早安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在開班會之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.52,0:12:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師有個建議要對大家說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}第24回舞島馬拉松大會\N招募參加者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.92,0:13:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的舞島馬拉松 大家一起參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要大家都去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.51,0:13:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.82,0:13:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.09,0:13:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經替大家送出申請了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油喔~喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.71,0:13:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就在馬拉松中合而為一吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師 夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.46,0:13:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通點就行了 普通點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是在演電視劇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.49,0:13:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點沉重了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.79,0:13:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉重？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.40,0:13:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 為什麼還來找我商量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.66,0:13:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還那樣開心的和我說笑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.41,0:13:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會被說成像反派一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.45,0:13:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們要被罵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這老師挺危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在成為真正的教師之前能看清現實對她來說也是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:22.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 長瀨也居然會搭理你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.18,0:14:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明對你們這些滿身是BUG的人做什麼都是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡宅男 你剛才在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪得到你在這說大話嗎 不過是遊戲狂熱者而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.72,0:14:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 眼鏡宅男呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.83,0:14:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到哪裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙 到哪裡都無所謂了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.83,0:14:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}41 42 43 44 45
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 這課怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.66,0:15:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 很不妙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 都太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是為了大家才這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.27,0:15:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 要是大家能同心協力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳為什麼要來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡不是只有不愉快的回憶嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.33,0:15:50.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是令人討厭的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你才是我這次失敗的起點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.84,0:15:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次本來一定會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經成為大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也學習了很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會成為理想中的老師的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然妳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.75,0:16:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳和以前一樣什麼都沒改變
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不要 不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.64,0:16:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說了 不要說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.95,0:16:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳不管是以前還是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是將自己的理想強加於別人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.68,0:16:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.70,0:16:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話我該怎麼做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.20,0:17:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我除了努力什麼都不會 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.61,0:17:18.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,越是努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家越是離我遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明是想要幫助大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該怎麼做才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.36,0:17:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.62,0:17:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將理想更加強硬地塞給別人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.21,0:17:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要理會別人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳只要做妳內心認為正確的事就夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不會跟著來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.68,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在面對理想時 大家都會感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不行的 不可能做到的」這樣想著而逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.07,0:18:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是現實的屏障
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.02,0:18:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此妳也必須去做
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管受到多大的傷 多麼孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.78,0:18:21.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也必須展現出妳的理想
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像巨漢鶴馬一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.93,0:18:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妳是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長瀨老師
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.12,0:18:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:18:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡 在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…老師 回教室去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們不對 我們道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同學們…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桂木同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.05,0:19:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾露西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我寫好了如何到達結局的順序
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.25,0:19:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要按照我寫著的那樣來辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:34.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.83,0:19:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在太任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 長瀨也居然會搭理你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明對你們這些滿身是BUG的人做什麼都是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.06,0:19:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長瀨出去之後 我會對班上的人惡言相向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將他們對長瀨的不滿重置
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.65,0:20:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而妳 在我出去之後
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.84,0:20:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}42 43 44 45
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.45,0:20:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數到500之後 將班上的人引到體育館
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.92,0:20:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長瀨老師 完全沒有回來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那麼讓人失落的事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:15.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,499 500
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.27,0:20:21.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起去迎接長瀨老師回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 大家說的太過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.85,0:20:29.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 同類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧 我知道長瀨老師會在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然覺得稍微有點強硬的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.61,0:20:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家都來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是強硬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.42,0:20:48.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於現實 只有理想是不夠的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.47,0:20:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.87,0:20:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想的結局也是需要的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定會成為一個好老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:20.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,長瀨老師的教育實習 也到今天結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:21.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知為什麼神大人他
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.22,0:21:26.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從那天以後就再也沒來過學校
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.12,0:21:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是受您照顧了 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.56,0:21:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢 有什麼煩惱的話就來和我傾訴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.86,0:21:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會聽妳說的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.50,0:21:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.63,0:22:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為再也見不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.54,0:22:18.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.31,0:22:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.18,0:22:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還以為你是個孤獨而且冷淡的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.26,0:22:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.25,0:22:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.28,0:22:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要 再回來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我會成為更棒的老師然後回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.38,0:22:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.82,0:22:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看到我不像老師的一面 這次是最後一次了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.03,0:23:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來那個遊魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.43,0:23:20.06,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}FLAG 11.0 將太陽永存於心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.06,0:23:35.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}FLAG 12.0 夏日大作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.16,0:23:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,製作好遊戲的條件是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.63,0:23:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像天使一樣大膽地將故事展開
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.58,0:23:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像惡魔一樣纖細地把握住平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將人類的靈魂注入角色中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.09,0:23:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相對的製作出爛遊戲的理由是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.31,0:23:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉 有各式各樣的原因啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.83,0:23:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡魔是很纖細的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.32,0:02:05.52,logo,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,400)}{\pos(596,352)}雪酷字幕组
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:42.20,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:42.20,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我不願讓機會溜走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:45.45,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:45.45,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}為什麼要剝奪我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:48.09,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Reason as against emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.61,0:00:48.09,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}與感性不同 理性更讓我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:52.92,OPen1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.09,0:00:52.92,OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}必須跨越這挫敗感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.42,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.09,0:00:56.42,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}所有努力將不會是徒勞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:59.49,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Endless desire,like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.42,0:00:59.49,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無盡的慾望 在心中不斷反復
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:02.80,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Such a pain,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.52,0:01:02.80,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}夾在理想與現實間的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:05.33,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}There is a way to change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.80,0:01:05.33,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一定有一種可以改變世界的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:06.90,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.36,0:01:06.90,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是的 交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:10.20,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.93,0:01:10.20,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我歌唱得走調又如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.28,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:12.28,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}手繪不佳也無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:17.04,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:17.04,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我只會為了追尋那唯一的信念而行動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.69,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.69,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.69,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}克服你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:18.69,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Overcome myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:22.03,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}“A whole new world god only knows”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.88,0:01:22.03,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}"一個只有神知道的嶄新的世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.93,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:26.23,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\pos(424,440)\fs22}I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.10,0:01:24.93,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我將永遠伴君左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.35,0:01:26.23,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs22}我明白你內心受到的傷害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.13,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}To be a knight,to be a light for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:28.13,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}做你的騎士 做你的明燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:29.57,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.13,0:01:29.57,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們會無比閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:30.12,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.57,0:01:30.12,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.23,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}No more tears,everything works out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.12,0:01:32.23,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不再需要眼淚 我們將不再懼怕任何事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:34.76,OPen2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}That's "God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.23,0:01:34.76,OPCN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}那就是所謂的“只有神知道”
